<plot>When is a stranger no longer a stranger? The Atwood Stories explore the moment when a chance meeting becomes something more. Although each story is unique and unrelated in character and setting, a stream of random encounters occurs throughout the anthology, involving people who dare to reach out. In addition to Polarities, the stories include Betty, The Man From Mars, Death by Landscape, Isis and The Sunrise.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?541197</url></doc>
